{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u83420aff\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FADB14\">注意:</span></strong><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">当前插入的链接如果是</span></strong><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FADB14\">分享链接（带share的）</span></strong><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">以及</span></strong><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FADB14\">编辑状态下的链接（带edit的）</span></strong><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，是不会在知识网络中展示的。</span></strong></p><p id=\"uf78d09ab\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u3122a03c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">为什么我们需要关联知识？</span></p><p id=\"u906c5a6c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">我们鼓励每个用户，在语雀中构建自己的数字花园。</span></p><p id=\"u2f03ebad\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">数字花园是什么呢？是信息流，是由灵感变为的小记，文档和知识库等。</span></p><p id=\"u896c4e4d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">除了知识库和团队的结构外，语雀还提供知识网络的能力，让知识可以跨越组织地关联到一起，形成一张知识网络。</span></p><h1 id=\"OiTrT\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在文档中建立知识关联</span></h1><h3 id=\"RHF8j\"><span class=\"ne-text\">粘贴语雀链接</span></h3><p id=\"ucae5e6f4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在文档中，通过直接粘贴链接的方式，构建知识关联。</span></p><p id=\"u7013c7e3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持四种形式的链接：原链接、标题形态、卡片形态、嵌入形态。</span></p><table id=\"AlQCY\" class=\"ne-table no-border\" style=\"width: 677px\"><tbody><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"87\"><p id=\"ucd636b6b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">链接形态</span></p></td><td width=\"590\"><p id=\"u0ece3941\" class=\"ne-p\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines</span></a></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"87\"><p id=\"u9f8e29c1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">标题形态</span></p></td><td width=\"590\"><p id=\"u6654d70d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span id=\"TzfcC\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines</a></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"87\"><p id=\"u8265aa34\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">卡片形态</span></p></td><td width=\"590\"><div id=\"FaKIv\" class=\"ne-yuque\">此处为语雀内容卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines</a></div></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"87\"><p id=\"ua0d13ff2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">嵌入形态</span></p></td><td width=\"590\"><div id=\"nsBXi\" class=\"ne-yuque\">此处为语雀内容卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines</a></div></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id=\"DhHDG\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过 @ 提及</span></h3><p id=\"u4ceb8e69\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在正文中输入 </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #F5F5F5\">@</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #BFBFBF; background-color: #F5F5F5\">提及</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> ，可提及语雀内容和人。可搜索到你访问的语雀内容范围。本知识库、本团队优先显示。</span></p><p id=\"ud59ddd02\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655193995304-4f295c67-a2b0-4198-a59f-da1ed782d3b9.png\" width=\"363\" id=\"ufcb56701\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655187544348-62072849-a6ec-46b5-844c-0971e7234a16.png\" width=\"366\" id=\"u05a029b7\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h3 id=\"U9WUp\"><span class=\"ne-text\">引入语雀内容</span></h3><p id=\"u3e0aca7e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过左上角加号面板</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655186849939-164bcd8f-aa6b-4654-83c0-5370d0fe7e27.png\" width=\"17\" id=\"u59bd08bc\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">，或斜杠输入</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/语雀内容</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，可快速搜索插入内容。</span></p><p id=\"u388b1122\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655187070047-f3b41c1e-f935-493c-8920-19ec85ba56ef.png\" width=\"302\" id=\"u626dce1a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u5f68a757\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655187284966-53878a89-731b-4305-a76f-fbc6184088aa.png\" width=\"774\" id=\"ud13ca39d\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ua79ec877\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">具体详见 </span><span id=\"AntBH\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/aint7x\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/aint7x</a></span></p><h1 id=\"K1itS\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在阅读页查看知识网络</span></h1><p id=\"u1dfb0600\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">发布文档后，可以在文档右上角点击查看知识网络。</span></p><p id=\"u9e4661c9\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655197244891-7afde77a-056a-4a42-8039-e3a68b8dfc7a.png\" width=\"896\" id=\"ub2560030\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ue0bdebfd\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击知识网络，可查看本篇文档引用过和被引用的语雀内容列表。</span></p><p id=\"ua6695632\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655197522060-2927d44f-4720-47a4-bf01-ff3e814e27f3.png\" width=\"1269\" id=\"ufb944314\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u1370d764\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655197593170-5f15e30c-7960-4359-bc37-87e903a44512.png\" width=\"750\" id=\"u6ff1bee9\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h1 id=\"ZNeq4\"><span class=\"ne-text\">更多</span></h1><p id=\"ub4e114c8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">未来我们将致力于让更多的语雀内容纳入知识网络。也在探索知识网络在更多的上下工程平台的多端同步和连接。</span></p><p id=\"ufac7e589\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果你有关于知识网络和双向链接更好的想法，或有什么疑问，欢迎评论，或提交</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">反馈</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">，与我们联系。</span></p></div>",
